1 In 2028 1%
2 After 2029 0%."
3 SECTION 2.(e) Section 2(d) of this act is effective for taxable years beginning on
4 or after January 1, 2025. Section 2(a) through (c) of this act becomes effective July 1, 2025. The
5 remainder of this act is effective when it becomes law.
